what is c programing language ?
c language is a most powerful,popular compiler type programing language.
{ c language ek bahut hi poverful or popular compiler type language hai}

c language is devloped(invented) by dennis ritchie at bell labratory (bell lab) in 1972.
  { clanguage ko dennis ritchie ne 1972 main bell lab main bnaya tha}
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
history of c programing :
before c language there is BCPL language and then B lanhuage and then aftre c language 

BCPL (basic combined programing language)

 actually BCPL language and B language working upon assembly language so it difficult to understandso so dennis ritchie 
invented c programing language in 1972 (tranditional c programing)

in 1989 ANSI standarized c programing

ANSI : american national standard institute.

after standarized cprograming language know as a ANSI c, c89
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
features of c programing language :

c language is a easy to understand programing language - mother of all languages

c is a small becouse it contains only 32 keywords

c contain libaries
